{
  "stem": "23438.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We woke up to the sound of bombs falling on Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- actually, we were expecting something to happen for some months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that year, first September is the end of school holidays in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's the day children go back to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That summer my mother rented a house very close to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there was fear that something could happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we'd just come back from the holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were all ready for the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We thought there was something coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had gas masks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we all thought there would be a gas war, like in World War I.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we woke up to the sound of bombs falling on Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a shock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was something, those first few days, of a bit of an adventure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I had a very good friend that last-- last year, who I thought I was madly in love with, at my ripe age of 12.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I thought, all right, whatever happens, whenever he goes, I go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Let's be brave and fight our wars together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "On the 6 September, the German army was advancing on Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was an appeal by the city president for all men able to carry arms to leave the city and go east, to regroup there and be mobilized.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] My father's office had closed in the first couple of days of war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "His boss managed to go back to-- to France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He wanted my father to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But that was already impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Father got six months' salary as a sort of one-off payment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that's about the extent of what we were left with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So on the 6 September, father was leaving Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
